      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an impeccable E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos overhaul, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing is tight, the suspension geometry is factory-spec, and the paint depth remains consistent across all panels. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
